Implementation via Kryonet-Framework :: https://github.com/EsotericSoftware/kryonet

Network.java :: Includes register()-services & classes for Client & Server

GameServer & Listener :: Employ effective Servermanagement using Kryonet
        Serversetup in MainMenuScreen using hardcoded TCP & UDP-Ports. For Libgdx, only TCP really matters.
                GameServer server = new GameServer(6000, 6001);
                server.startServer();

GameClient & Listener :: Employ effective Clientmanagement using Krynet
        Clientsetup in ConnectionScreen using hardcoded TCP & UDP-Ports aswell as Timeout-Factor.
                GameClient client = new GameClient(6000, 6001, 10000);
        The actual connection requires an IP-Address to connect to.
                final String ip = eIPText.getText();
                client.connect(ip);